				<h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title"><span id="addComment">Add a comment</span><p>Your email address will not be published.<br /><span>All fields are required to comment.</span></p> <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/theedge/2013/09/24/travel-abroad-summer-2013-patrick-henry-colombia/#respond" style="display:none;">Cancel reply</a></small></h3>
									<form action="http://blogs.roanoke.com/theedge/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form">
